Package: nhgCI
Title: Confidence Intervals for Negative Hypergeometric Parameters
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Rachel", "Roggenkemper", email = "rroggenk@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides functions to construct short exact confidence intervals for two of the parameters of 
    negative hypergeometric distribution: (i) the number of successes (M) and (ii) the population 
    size (N). Implements the following methods: Analog to the Clopper-Pearson, Conditional Minimal 
    Cardinality (CMC), CG (Crow & Gardner), and Blaker.
